### Bug 7 (CONFIRMED, HIGH CONFIDENCE): `RocketLayer` runs a `setInterval` at 16ms to update `timeRef.current`, but this interval is NEVER cleared when the component unmounts during `universeMode` switches

**File:** `C:\Users\johnm\iskrib_v3\client\src\components\Universe\layers\RocketLayer.jsx`, lines 24-30

```js
